OL,3,CMounting plastic problems in Guernsey
OL,4,Ctrigger public warnings
OL,6,FA Guernsey charity is asking islanders
OL,7,Fto think twice before throwing, after
OL,8,Frecording a rise in the amount of
OL,9,Fplastic waste washing up on the
OL,10,Fisland's shores.
OL,12,FThe Clean Earth Trust's latest report
OL,13,Freveals that over 600 kilograms of
OL,14,Fmarine litter appeared on Guernsey's
OL,15,Fbeaches in 2024, with over 80% of it
OL,16,Fbeing plastic.
OL,18,FThe document compiles findings from
OL,19,Fthe charity's weekly surveyed beach
OL,20,Fcleans.
