OL,6,FPlastic pieces, cigarette butts,
OL,7,Fnurdles (little plastic pellets), and
OL,8,Ffood and drink wrappers were amongst
OL,9,Fthose items most commonly found - with
OL,10,Fthe charity estimating nearly 40% of
OL,11,Flitter originated from the public.
OL,13,FFor example, 136 food wrappers were
OL,14,Ffound on Vazon during a single
OL,15,Fmorning's beach clean.
OL,17,FMeanwhile, they estimate that around
OL,18,F12% of the overall waste was from
OL,19,Ffishing and just 1.3% from shipping.
