OL,3,CMounting plastic problems in Guernsey
OL,4,Ctrigger public warnings
OL,6,FThe group's findings come after
OL,7,FGuernsey Waste has issued warnings
OL,8,Fasking households to take more care
OL,9,Fwhen recycling their plastics, because
OL,10,Fthe number of blue recycling bags
OL,11,Ffound to be contaminated is on the
OL,12,Frise.
OL,14,FParish recycling collectors are being
OL,15,Fforced to leave behind bags containing
OL,16,Funrecyclable materials - such as thin-
OL,17,Ffilm plastic items or dirty containers
OL,18,Fwith food residue still inside.
