OL,3,CMounting plastic problems in Guernsey
OL,4,Ctrigger public warnings
OL,6,FPaul Bugden, Clean Earth Trust's
OL,7,FPolicy Officer, says this kind of
OL,8,Fcarelessness does have an impact
OL,9,Ffurther down the line.
OL,11,F"The more we can recycle, the better",
OL,12,Fhe says, "that obviously helps keep it
OL,13,Fout of the waste stream, out of the
OL,14,Fenvironment.
OL,16,F"Fundamentally, what we're trying to
OL,17,Fdo is stop harming wildlife - because
OL,18,Fif our fish and our birds are
OL,19,Fingesting plastic, that is basically
OL,20,Fkilling them."
