OL,4,Ctrigger public warnings
OL,6,FSarah Robinson, Guernsey Waste's
OL,7,FOperations Manager, says whilst they
OL,8,Fdo what they can to dispose of
OL,9,Fcontaminated bags in an
OL,10,Fenvironmentally-friendly way, the
OL,11,Fpublic needs to be better at sorting
OL,12,Ftheir waste themselves.
OL,14,F"It doesn't go to landfill thankfully,
OL,15,Fit does go off for energy recovery",
OL,16,Fshe explains, "but obviously that is
OL,17,Fat the bottom of the waste hierarchy,
OL,18,Fand we really want to be capturing as
OL,19,Fmuch recycling as we possibly can.
