OL,6,F"The good news is that hopefully in
OL,7,Ftime to come, the plastic will be
OL,8,Frecyclable", Sarah adds, "but the
OL,9,Fcapacity in the markets at the moment
OL,10,Fisn't quite that fortunate.
OL,12,F"But we hope that someday in the near
OL,13,Ffuture, we'll be able to say yes -
OL,14,Fthis will be recycled too."
